comments: Brown (BOS) draws Brogdon (IND) into the air towards him and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Wanamaker (BOS) establishes himself in Holiday's (IND) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Walker (BOS) makes marginal contact with Warren (IND) during his natural shooting motion.
Turner (IND) and Theis (BOS) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Ojeleye (BOS) maintains his legal guarding position as he defends Brogdon (IND) and does not affect his SQBR.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Warren (IND) and does not deliver contact.
Holiday (IND) makes contact to Tatum's (BOS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Walker (BOS) places a hand to the front of Brogdon (IND) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) does not make contact with Warren (IND) during his contest on the jump shot attempt.
Walker (BOS) briefly grasps and releases Sabonis' (IND) shorts during the rebound without affecting his ability to maintain position.
Holiday (IND) initiates the contact by moving into Wanamaker's (BOS) body, affecting his SQBR. This contact occurs prior to any contact from Wanamaker.
Wanamaker (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball during Sabonis' (IND) drive.
Theis (BOS) makes marginal contact as he contests Sabonis' (IND) shot attempt in the post.
Sabonis (IND) makes arm contact with Tatum (BOS) during his drive but does not affect his SQBR.
Although Holiday (IND) is drawn into the air, he maintains verticality as Wanamaker (BOS) initiates the contact during the driving shot attempt.
Green (BOS) makes body contact with Brogdon (IND) at the start of his drive.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in Warren's (IND) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.
Walker (BOS) makes marginal contact with Brogdon (IND) as he receives the inbounds pass.
Theis (BOS) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
Williams (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Warren (IND) and does not deliver contact.
Warren (IND) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Walker (BOS) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) does not establish himself in Edwards' (BOS) path as he delivers contact during the screen.
Williams (BOS) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
